      "content": "helplines just give me scripts. they don't get how heavy it actually is. it’s not just a \"bad day\" or feeling down. it’s like the air is made of lead and i'm just... done. how am i supposed to go on living a life that feels this hollow? i just want the silence to mean something instead of just being empty.",
